name: People Only Exist In Our Mind
description:
(Heavenly Way To Die) series. 

Some people may ask what situation they are in and most of them don't realize it, take a deeper look and learn that every level in life influences human behavior and the traces left behind. unite every strategy in life according to its place and level on a strange paper chessboard.

Experimental Media Collage 
Digital & Analog (21x30cm)
